  "title": "Beauty Therapist #77339",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Beauty & Wellness</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Beauty Therapist</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard Road</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, 10am – 8pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3000 (Basic) + Commission + Employee Discounts + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Administer various beauty services, such as facials and body treatments, including other specialized services.</li><li>Conduct personalized consultations to evaluate client needs and devise customized treatment strategies.</li><li>Uphold excellent standards of cleanliness and hygiene in the treatment areas.</li><li>Ensure the comfort and satisfaction of clients from start to finish of the service.</li><li>Promote our range of products and services actively to clients.</li><li>Engage in regular training and professional development sessions to keep abreast of the latest industry practices and technologies.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1-2 years of professional experience in a beauty therapist role.</li><li>Additional experience in body treatments will be considered an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77339 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
